                     </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <p>The first fifty folios are copiously annotated in Persian in minute nastaʿlīq script between ff1-51. Across the MS there are some lines which have been vocalised.</p>
                  </additions>
                  <bindingDesc>
                     <p>Red leather binding with floral design on the spine.</p>
                  </bindingDesc>
